834
01:16:38,051 --> 01:16:39,249
Come on.

835
01:16:44,057 --> 01:16:45,468
Come on.

836
01:16:51,898 --> 01:16:53,273
Brian?

837
01:16:56,361 --> 01:16:58,567
All right, get the fuck out.

838
01:17:34,066 --> 01:17:36,058
Get off of me!

839
01:17:36,151 --> 01:17:38,144
Stop it! Stop!

840
