849
01:19:34,437 --> 01:19:36,228
Why the hell not?

850
01:19:36,939 --> 01:19:39,311
Because I know Adam.

851
01:19:41,068 --> 01:19:43,642
He's no angel, but he's not a murderer.

852
01:19:43,738 --> 01:19:47,570
