884
01:24:03,290 --> 01:24:04,785
Still here.

885
01:24:05,584 --> 01:24:09,368
I heard a noise.
I thought something happened to Dorothy.

886
01:24:10,965 --> 01:24:13,041
Dorothy's a big girl.

887
01:24:14,927 --> 01:24:16,505
