-Stay away from me!
-Come on.

918
01:29:54,811 --> 01:29:57,480
-Adam, I'm sorry.
-It's all right.

919
01:29:58,022 --> 01:29:59,730
I'm so sorry!

920
01:29:59,899 --> 01:30:02,390
All right. It's over.

921
01:30:03,736 --> 01:30:05,065
